+## 2026-07-17 Australia/Sydney - ADP V0.1 task ADP-S5-P04-T068 (Knowledge Validity + 131-item benefit-parity regression; NOT_DEPLOYED)
+
+- Sixty-eighth task of the ADP V0.1 FINAL EXECUTION program -- closes S5-P04 and Stage S5. When a source's substantive content changes, old knowledge is automatically re-opened (marked needs_review / invalid) and can be re-learned; and every one of 131 competitor user-benefit items has a definite status and a named owner, so no benefit is left in an unknown / nobody-owns-it limbo. release_mode NOT_DEPLOYED; a read-only library, the production worker/cron/data untouched. New tool arxiv-daily-push/docs/pursuing_goal/v0_1/tools/knowledge_validity.py: make_knowledge (binds knowledge to its source's T026 content_hash), check_validity (a substantive source change -> needs_review, a removed source -> invalid, a noise-only re-render -> stays valid, never in-place mutation), revalidate (re-learn: re-bind to the new version), and parity_report (every item's status is in a closed vocabulary with no 'unknown', every owner is real with no 'no-owner', delivered/partial cite evidence and planned/not_applicable give a reason). Deliverables under arxiv-daily-push/docs/pursuing_goal/v0_1/evidence/ADP-S5-P04-T068/: parity_registry_131.json, knowledge_validity_report.json, known_gaps.md, and adversarial_review.md (review CONFIRMED_SOUND). Acceptance verified (evidence/ADP-S5-P04-T068/test-results/knowledge_validity_tests.txt, ACCEPTANCE = PASS, exit 0): the validity clock is hash-driven (a noise-only re-render shares the bound content_hash and stays valid = no churn; a substantive change auto-flips to needs_review; a removed source -> invalid; revalidate re-binds to the new version's hash); the parity registry has exactly 131 items with zero unknown-status, zero no-owner, and zero delivered/partial items missing evidence (by_status delivered 92 / partial 21 / planned 15 / not_applicable 3); statuses are honest (delivered cites a real ADP task; benefits whose substrate exists but is not fully built are conservatively marked partial; NOT_DEPLOYED library-layer disclaimer stated); and a gate control injecting an 'unknown' status, a 'no-owner', a blank owner, a bad status token, and a note-less planned item catches all of them. Realtime not regressed (no deploy, live build b189d3cc0703 == T040). Cost (unknown != 0): production new_requests 0, D1 0, R2 0, model_calls 0. Ends IMPLEMENTATION_READY_FOR_INDEPENDENT_VERIFICATION.
+
 ## 2026-07-17 Australia/Sydney - ADP V0.1 task ADP-S5-P04-T067 (Library / notes / Provenance export; NOT_DEPLOYED)
 
 - Sixty-seventh task of the ADP V0.1 FINAL EXECUTION program (S5-P04). Makes reading and evidence a long-term asset (not something that only exists in Today): a user saves items into a Library with notes and collections and exports to Markdown/CSV/JSON, and every exported entry carries its full provenance -- the original URL, the version, the fetch time, the claim evidence, and a license notice. release_mode NOT_DEPLOYED; a read-only library, the production worker/cron/data untouched. New tool arxiv-daily-push/docs/pursuing_goal/v0_1/tools/library_export.py: add_to_library (refuses to save an item without complete provenance), provenance_complete (all five fields present and non-empty; blank/whitespace counts as missing), export_markdown/export_csv/export_json (each carries all provenance fields per entry; refuses to export an entry with incomplete provenance). Deliverables under arxiv-daily-push/docs/pursuing_goal/v0_1/evidence/ADP-S5-P04-T067/: library_export_report.json, export_sample.{md,csv,json}, known_gaps.md, and adversarial_review.md (review CONFIRMED_SOUND). Acceptance verified (evidence/ADP-S5-P04-T067/test-results/library_export_tests.txt, ACCEPTANCE = PASS, exit 0): every one of the three export formats carries all five provenance fields (source_url, version, fetched_at, claim_evidence, license) for every entry -- checked per-entry in JSON, per-row in CSV, and per-entry-block in Markdown; a license notice is present in all three formats; comma/quote/newline values round-trip losslessly through CSV; JSON round-trips provenance unchanged; and an entry with incomplete provenance is refused on save AND on export in all three formats. Realtime not regressed (no deploy, live build b189d3cc0703 == T040). Cost (unknown != 0): production new_requests 0, D1 0, R2 0, model_calls 0. Ends IMPLEMENTATION_READY_FOR_INDEPENDENT_VERIFICATION.
