+```text
+Task: ADP-S5-P04-T068
+Commit: <记于提交步骤，见 changed_files.txt / git 历史>
+Files changed: tools/knowledge_validity.py(新) + T068 证据包(含131项registry) + 治理同步（见 changed_files.txt）；无 worker/生产改动
